These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, spy, animation, sports
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, jazz, ambient, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: french, dutch, russian, australian
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, roller, quad-bike, bike
1. the dutch is the fan of pop##1
2. the russian is between the person watching animation movies and the person watching sports movies##2
3. the dutch is the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the fan of country is on the left of the french##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is the person watching animation movies##1
7. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
8. the french is on the far right##1
9. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | sports   | romance  | animation  |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | pop    | country      | ambient    |
| Nationality   | australian | dutch | russian | french |
| Transport     | bike  | scooter       | roller    | quad-bike     |

