.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, puzzles, card-games, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts, epic, drama
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, snake, ferret, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, surfing, rowing, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the pony is the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the person watching drama movies is between the owner of the ferret and the person who's sport is cycling##2
6. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person watching drama movies and the owner of the pony##2
7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
9. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | puzzles    | card-games  | baking    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary      | martial-arts  | drama  | epic |
| Pet           | pony      | ferret       | snake      | chinchilla       |
| Sport         | surfing    | badminton | rowing | cycling |

