2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the firefighter##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the mechanic is the person who's hobby is chess##1
7. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
8. the person eating corn is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is chess##2
9. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person eating kiwi and the mechanic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | apricot | kiwi     | corn   | apple     |
| Hobby       | video-games   | hiking   | drawing | chess |
| Job         | social-worker   | software-developer | firefighter       | mechanic    |
| Transport   | trike    | taxi | ship  | quad-bike    |

