 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching family movies is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person watching epic movies is the photographer##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 9. the engineer is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
10. the dressmaker is between the owner of the cat and the videographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | engineer  | videographer | dressmaker     | photographer |
| Movie-Genre   | family | drama  | animation | epic       |
| Pet           | chinchilla       | goat    | guinea-pig      | cat           |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing   | cycling   | swimming         |

