 3. the project-manager is the person eating tomato##1
 4. the project-manager is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
 6. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 7. the accountant is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 8. the engineer is the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the person eating pumpkin is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person watching drama movies##2
10. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
