3. the canadian is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the malaysian##2
4. the mechanic is on the left of the malaysian##1
5. the canadian is the canadian##1
6. the malaysian is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the malaysian is on the left of the security-guard##1
8. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
9. the fan of house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
