4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the motorbike and the person watching thriller movies##2
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
