.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, cola, milk
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, pomegranate, lemon, cranberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, singing, reading, rock-climbing
4 different pets are kept: fish, lizard, frog, bird
 1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 4. the person eating broccoli is the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the owner of the bird is between the person eating broccoli and the person eating lemon##2
 9. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
10. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person eating broccoli and the person eating lemon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta    | cola    | milk      | soy-milk |
| Food       | broccoli        | cranberry       | lemon       | pomegranate     |
| Hobby      | reading | chess | rock-climbing | singing        |
| Pet        | lizard       | bird     | frog         | fish           |

