 3. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 5. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the bird##2
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is the person eating radish##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the bird is the person driving the scooter##1
10. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person eating pumpkin##1

